divs: Sighting DetailsMe and my brother were riding bikes and i decided to take a picture to make sure the camera was working.so i took a picture and when we got home we put the picture onto the computer to look at it because the screen on the camera doesnt work anymore.so when we looked at it at first i thought it was 2 moons or something but it wasnt.then i looked and one looked saucer shaped and the other looked like the moon.so then me and my dad went up to that area and looked around for the moon in the object and saw neither.so i think that both may have been a u.f.o
Summary: spotted the objects in a camera picture my son took.
